title: Mint Music Radio - Blackberry
description:
Mint Music Radio is a global online radio station playing the newest international artists on Blackberry devices. MMR plays all genres of music including Rock, Hip-Hop, Classic Hindi, Bollywood, Pop, Religious and about 2000 additional categories.  Whether you're a Belgian fan of Claes's, a Calcutta fan of Arjyo Bala or a Ghanaian fan of Akoffena Difaya, Mint Music Radio has the artist that you love to hear.

Mint Music Radio is also an asset for music artists in need of radio exposure and radio royalties. Therefore if you are a musician, singer, a band for any other kind of music artist, feel FREE to join up at http://www.mintmusic.com/signup.

The purpose of Mint Music Radio is to provide Mint Music Artist with international exposure and radio royalties. So every time that you download, listen and share Mint Music Radio, you are helping to support independent artist all over the world. http://www.MintMusicRadio.com
